column2: Wooden cabin with sea view located in the Danish nature. Isolated and with private campfire site.
Wooden cabin with sea view located in the Danish nature. Isolated and with private campfire site.
Our  house is just down to the Great Belt. There are beds for 10 adults, 1 guest bed, 3 junior beds plus a baby bed.
Enjoy the tranquility and hang out in the giant garden overlooking the water. Or take a canoe or SUP and explore Isefjord.
